list.abstract: vegetable（英[ˈvedʒtəbl]，美[ˈvedʒtəbl]），英语单词，作名词为蔬菜；植物人，作形容词为蔬菜的；植物的。短语搭配有vegetable salad（蔬菜沙拉）。例句为“At the age of six, I could make vegetable salad.（六岁时，我会做蔬菜沙拉。）” 该单词的复数形式为vegetables，作名词时近义词为plant、greenstuff，作形容词时近义词为floral、botanic。

yingyinNormal.en: Roll up, roll up. For the vegetable roundabout swing things. A vegetable roundabout swing thing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 摇起来，转起来！各位小朋友都快来坐蔬菜转专椅。来吧！可以坐蔬菜转转椅咯！

yingyinNormal.en: This is Grandpa Pig's vegetable garden. He has grown all these vegetables himself!
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是猪爷爷的蔬菜园。他自己种了所有这些蔬菜！

yingyinNormal.en: This is Grandpa Pig's vegetable garden. He has grown all these vegetables himself!
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是猪爷爷的蔬菜园。他自己种了所有这些蔬菜！

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. Stop, Peppa. Vegetable peelings don't go in the normal bin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的。等一下，佩奇。蔬菜皮不能直接扔进普通的垃圾桶。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. Stop, Peppa. Vegetable peelings don't go in the normal bin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的。等一下，佩奇。蔬菜皮不能直接扔进普通的垃圾桶。

yingyinNormal.en: My vegetable and ham wraps and five spice chicken drumsticks. First the chicken.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的蔬菜火腿卷和五香鸡腿。首先来做鸡腿。

yingyinNormal.en: Next, just add good vegetable stock or you can use chicken stock, and then give it a good stir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 接下来加入蔬菜高汤或者鸡汤，然后充分搅匀。

yingyinNormal.en: Fresh vegetable stock. This is a good cheat, or you can use you know the cubed vegetable stock. You can get these in the supermarket, just pour that on top.
yingyinNormal.zh: 新鲜蔬菜汤料。偷懒的好方法，你也可以用块状的，能在超市买到，浇在上面。

yingyinNormal.en: I knew we should have stayed together. Now look at us. Stuck in a giant vegetable jail.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就知道我们该待在一起，看我们现在困在这个巨大的蔬菜监狱里。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.zh: 胡萝卜不是水果。哦。胡萝卜是蔬菜。爱德曼是一只聪明的大象。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: Duan Jiayang, a 12-year-old student of a primary school in Yinchuan, Ningxia, learns the skills required to take care of <highlight>vegetable</highlight> fields.
